Memo - Mapping wells and HOLC-graded neighborhoods

Purpose

The goal of this notebook is to practice importing and mapping Enverus wells and HOLC grading data. We import Enverus wells data and HOLC neighborhood grades, converts the wells data to a sf object, and then set up to map them on top of one another.

Danesha, please make any edits and practice so youre confident with these functions. Your homework is to make a map of wells and HOLC neighborhoods in Los Angeles. Youll need to use the filter , st_as_sf, and ggplot functions. Remember, with GitHub we can always go back to older versions, so you cant break anything! -DG
